The published container image (ghcr.io/drowzeys/dspark-nvfp4-stage-c) is a
convenience build for reproduction. It is layered on top of aidendle94's
GB10 sparkrun-vllm-ds4 runtime base and therefore includes upstream COMPILED
layers (aidendle94's patched flashinfer / DeepGEMM kernels, Rafael Caricio's
DSpark overlay). These are redistributed here with credit, under their
respective upstream licenses; all attribution is in CREDITS.md. If any upstream
author prefers the image not be redistributed, open an issue and it will be
removed and replaced with the docs/BUILD.md build-from-source path.
